.confirmation
	.inline
		h2(translate="HEADING_ARE_YOU_SURE") Are you sure you want to continue?
		|         
		p(translate="TXT_NO_UNDO") Please keep in mind you cannot undo this action.
		|         
		ul
			li(translate="TXT_TOPIC_ACCESS_REMOVED") You cannot participate in the Topic any more.
			|             
			li(translate="TXT_TOPIC_ACCESS_ADMIN_CAN_ADD_BACK") Topic administrator can add you back later if needed.
