		.buttons
			button.button.highlight-5(ng-click="closeThisDialog()", translate="BTN_NO_LEAVE") NO, DON'T LEAVE THE TOPIC
			|             
			button.button.highlight-4(ng-click="confirm()", translate="BTN_YES_LEAVE") YES, LEAVE THE TOPIC
